                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d614">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Taylor</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Gresham</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Madrid</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1894-05-29">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 29, 1894</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mr. Taylor informs the Department that in an interview with the minister for
                    foreign affairs on the 29th instant, he promised to go in person to the minister
                    for the colonies and demand that Spanish repertory take effect at once.</p>
            </div>
